{{香港航空}}
'''皇家香港輔助空軍'''（{{lang-en|The '''R'''oyal '''H'''ong '''K'''ong '''A'''uxiliary '''A'''ir '''F'''orce}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：'''RHKAAF'''）是[[英屬香港|英屬香港]]的[[空軍|空軍]]<ref name="b9780953034512-173-176">{{cite book |title=Royal Air Force Reserve and Auxiliary Forces - RAF Museum |date=2003 |publisher=RAF Museum |location=UK |isbn=9780953034512 |page=173-176 |url=https://www.rafmuseum.org.uk/documents/research/RAF-Historical-Society-Journals/Journal-29A-Seminar-Reserve-Auxiliary-Forces.pdf |access-date=11 January 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016172859/https://www.rafmuseum.org.uk/documents/research/RAF-Historical-Society-Journals/Journal-29A-Seminar-Reserve-Auxiliary-Forces.pdf |archive-date=2015-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="flightglobal-1981-2518">{{cite book |title=FlightGlobal (1981) Hong Kong |date=1981 |publisher=FlightGlobal |location=UK |page=346 |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1981/1981%20-%202518.html?search=Royal%20Hong%20Kong%20Auxiliary%20Air%20Force |accessdate=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220003103/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1981/1981%20-%202518.html?search=Royal%20Hong%20Kong%20Auxiliary%20Air%20Force |archive-date=2019-02-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，成立於1949年<ref name="legco-1992">{{cite web |title=立法局會議過程正式紀錄 - 立法會 |url=https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr91-92/chinese/lc_sitg/hansard/h920527.pdf |publisher=香港立法會 |accessdate=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205062129/https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr91-92/chinese/lc_sitg/hansard/h920527.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，屬於香港政府部門之一，並為[[政府飛行服務隊|政府飛行服務隊]]的前身<ref name="海陸空搜救隨時候命">{{cite news |title=飛行服務隊 海陸空搜救隨時候命 |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2423516/%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%20%E6%B5%B7%E9%99%B8%E7%A9%BA%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%91%BD |accessdate=2020-12-26 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2019-08-12 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930212804/https://topick.hket.com/article/2423516/%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E9%9A%8A%20%E6%B5%B7%E9%99%B8%E7%A9%BA%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%91%BD |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 概要 ==
香港本地軍隊於1970年進行改組，成立於1948年的[[皇家香港軍團|皇家香港防衛軍]]（[[英文|英文]]：Royal Hong Kong Defence Force，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：RHKDF）解散，其轄下的空軍單位「香港輔助空軍」成為獨立部隊<ref name="gwulo-hkaaf">{{cite web |title=HKAAF |url=https://gwulo.com/atom/19742 |publisher=Gwulo: Old Hong Kong |accessdate=2020-04-10 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008174447/https://gwulo.com/atom/19742 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並獲英女皇[[伊利沙伯二世|伊利沙伯二世]]授予「[[皇家|皇家]]」名銜，以繼承皇家香港防衛軍解散後的榮譽，因而命名為「皇家香港輔助空軍」<ref name="香港輔助空軍織章">{{cite news |title=【香港之翼 隨時候命】香港輔助空軍織章 |url=https://www.watershedhk.com/%E3%80%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E7%BF%BC-%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%91%BD%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%E7%B9%94%E7%AB%A0/ |accessdate=2021-12-31 |work=Watershed Hong Kong |date=2021-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211231181420/https://www.watershedhk.com/%e3%80%90%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%b9%8b%e7%bf%bc-%e9%9a%a8%e6%99%82%e5%80%99%e5%91%bd%e3%80%91%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%bc%94%e5%8a%a9%e7%a9%ba%e8%bb%8d%e7%b9%94%e7%ab%a0/ |archive-date=2021-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。皇家香港輔助空軍的軍徽主體為一條以飛機螺旋槳為背景的飛龍的八角形盾徽<ref name="RHKAAF-badge">{{cite web |title=badge, headdress, Royal Hong Kong Auxiliary Air Force |url=https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/30117282 |website=www.iwm.org.uk |publisher=Imperial War Museums |access-date=18 January 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118092303/https://www.iwm.org.uk/collections/item/object/30117282 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上方有大英君主的皇冠，而輔助空軍的格言「隨時候命」則以[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]（Semper Paratus）標示在盾徽的下方<ref name="britishempire-rhkaaf">{{cite web |title=Winged dragon: The history of the Royal Hong Kong Auxiliary Air Force |url=https://www.britishempire.co.uk/library/wingeddragon.htm |website=www.britishempire.co.uk |access-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209015501/https://www.britishempire.co.uk/library/wingeddragon.htm |archive-date=2020-02-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rhkaaf">{{cite web |title=Semper Paratus - "Always Prepared" |url=https://rhkaaf.hk/semper_paratus.php |website=rhkaaf.hk |accessdate=2021-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104093717/https://rhkaaf.hk/semper_paratus.php |archive-date=2021-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

皇家香港輔助空軍有別於[[駐港英軍|駐港英軍]]之中的[[英國皇家空軍|皇家空軍]]，雖然兩者當時都是以香港為根據地，但輔助空軍隸屬於香港政府，而駐港皇家空軍則由英國本土派駐來港，並由駐港英軍司令指揮。在成立初期的輔助空軍以兼職人員為主<ref name="飛足50年">{{cite news |title=輔助空軍司令係賓架　飛足50年 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/mobile/bkn-20171018060031999-1018_00822_001.html |accessdate=2020-10-24 |work=東方日報 |date=2017-10-18}}</ref>，屬於香港的[[後備軍事動員|後備軍]]，其指揮、調派及維持經費全由香港負責，除了保衛香港之外，輔助空軍還要承擔內部安全及救護任務，在1970年代以後，緊急醫療運送及搜救成為了輔助空軍的主要任務，而全職人員的比例亦漸漸增加。至於駐港皇家空軍則由駐港英軍司令指揮，主要負責香港防務，並由全職軍人組成。輔助空軍作為香港的後備軍，也經常參與駐港英軍舉行的演習，以準備支援駐港英軍執行保衛香港的任務，一旦香港發出戰時動員令，輔助空軍將歸由駐港英軍司令統一指揮<ref name="legco-1992"/>。

皇家香港輔助空軍於1988年起逐步擴大編制及全職化，以便在1990年代初接替駐港皇家空軍的工作<ref name="輔助空軍加强編制">{{cite news |title=耗資五億五千萬添置飛機 輔助空軍加强編制 逐步取替英軍工作 執行廿四小時搜索拯救任務 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqohuktLF698O%2F&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=13&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1990-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1999-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |accessdate=2021-01-11 |work=華僑日報 |date=1991-04-22 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113005057/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqohuktLF698O%2F&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=13&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1990-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1999-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1990年，輔助空軍計劃在1993年更名<ref name="將易名為政府飛行服務處">{{cite news |title=將易名為政府飛行服務處 皇家輔助空軍聘航空技術員 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJMMgiUKa672U&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1990-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1999-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |accessdate=2021-01-11 |work=華僑日報 |date=1990-11-29 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113131010/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJMMgiUKa672U&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1990-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1999-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並將各級[[軍階|軍階]]轉制為公務員職級<ref name="輔助空軍招聘新人-1991">{{cite news |title=輔助空軍招聘新人 會考及格月薪逾萬 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopIVJivglL4t&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=21&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1990-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1999-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |accessdate=2021-01-11 |work=華僑日報 |date=1991-10-16 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115001616/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqopIVJivglL4t&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=21&_coverpage_WAR_