8月4日清晨6時許，香港輔助空軍與駐港英軍及香港警察採取聯合行動<ref name="港英直升機空降圍剿">{{cite news |title=六七基地　港英直升機空降圍剿 |url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190925/P6CATWT6XBJIGMKCVS2URYCN7A/ |accessdate=2020-10-24 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2019-09-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623133603/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190925/P6CATWT6XBJIGMKCVS2URYCN7A/ |archivedate=2021-06-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，由當時正停泊在金鐘的皇家海軍[[競技神號航空母艦_(R12)|競技神號航空母艦]]派出三架{{tsl|en|Westland Whirlwind (helicopter)|韋斯特蘭旋風式直升機}}，運送警察空降到被鬥委會用作策動恐怖活動基地的北角僑冠大廈、新都城大廈及明園大廈<ref name="軍警空降華豐等大廈">{{cite news |title=直升機在今晨六時卅分 降落僑冠大廈 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFIQ8vUDxXrZm&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=25&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1960-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1969-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D |accessdate=2021-01-07 |work=工商晚報 |date=1967-08-04 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109004830/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%83%91%E5%86%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFIQ8vUDxXrZm&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=25&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%2